reviewText: Movie is ok. A bit pricy. Video definition is a little poor.

ALTHOUGH THIS WAS NOT AN ACTION FILM, OR HAS WELL KNOWN HOLLYWOOD ACTORS, EVERYONE I KNOW WHO HAS SEEN THIS FILM LOVES AND RECCOMENDS IT. iVE HAD A HARD TIME FINDING AN ORIGINAL DVD SO I'VE HAD TO RELAX MY STANDARDS AND BUY PIRATE COPIES TO GIVE AS GIFTS FOR ELDERLY STAY AT HOME FRIENDS.EVEN MY TEENAGE SON AND DAUGHTER ENJOYED IT AND HAVE TAKEN THEIR FRIENDS TO SEE IT (MEXICO CITY)
